---
import { allServices } from '../data/services';
const productTourHref = '/service/';
const contactHref = '/contact/';
const blogHref = '/blog/';

const logos = ['Sagara Technology', 'Ekrut', 'Lifepack', 'Datasintesa'];

const solutions = allServices.map(service => ({
  title: service.title,
  description: service.hero.subheading,
  features: service.solution.features.map(feature => feature.name),
  price: service.pricing.price,
  ctaLabel: 'Learn More',
  ctaHref: `/service/${service.slug}`
}));


const pricingTiers = [
  {
    name: 'Basic',
    description: '1 modul AI, 1 integrasi standar, pelaporan mingguan — Mulai Rp250.000 / bulan',
    highlight: false,
  },
  {
    name: 'Pro',
    description: '2 modul + CRM + analitik otomatis — Mulai Rp500.000 / bulan',
    highlight: true,
  },
  {
    name: 'Enterprise',
    description: 'Semua modul, orkestrasi multi-agen, SLA, pemberdayaan tim — Harga khusus',
    highlight: false,
  },
];
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-950 text-white">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-900/90 to-sky-900/60"></div>
    <div class="absolute -left-40 top-10 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-sky-500/20 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute -right-32 bottom-0 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/20 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto flex max-w-screen-xl flex-col gap-16 px-4 pb-28 pt-32 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:pt-40">
    <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-8 lg:flex-1">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/20 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
        Platform AI untuk tim operasi &amp; pertumbuhan
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
        Otomatisasi AI yang Memahami DNA Bisnis Anda
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-200">
        Selesaikan pekerjaan berulang, skalakan dukungan pelanggan, dan buka pendapatan baru dengan cetak biru otomatisasi yang dirancang untuk alur kerja Anda.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a
          href={productTourHref}
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 px-7 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-sky-900/40 transition hover:bg-sky-400 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-4 focus-visible:ring-sky-300"
        >
          Dapatkan Tur Produk
        </a>
        <a
          href={contactHref}
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/40 px-7 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white transition hover:border-white/60 hover:bg-white/10 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-4 focus-visible:ring-white/40"
        >
          Jadwalkan Panggilan Strategi
        </a>
      </div>
      <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm text-slate-200/80">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-sky-400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0110 10v1a5 5 0 01-5 5h-1a3 3 0 11-6 0H9a5 5 0 01-5-5v-1A10 10 0 0112 2zm0 2a8 8 0 00-8 8v1a3 3 0 003 3h1a1 1 0 011 1 1 1 0 002 0 1 1 0 011-1h1a3 3 0 003-3v-1a8 8 0 00-8-8z" /></svg>
          Strategi, implementasi, dan pemberdayaan perubahan dalam satu tim
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-sky-400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 4a2 2 0 012-2h4.5a2 2 0 011.414.586l7.5 7.5A2 2 0 0120 11.5V20a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-5a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V4z" /></svg>
          Integrasi di seluruh CRM, ERP, dan saluran yang sudah Anda gunakan
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="relative flex-1">
      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-xl overflow-hidden rounded-[2.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-3 shadow-[0_45px_120px_-50px_rgba(14,165,233,0.75)] backdrop-blur">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.25rem]">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556740749-887f6717d7e4?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
            alt="Dasbor otomatisasi AI"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-950/70 via-slate-900/10 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 left-1/2 hidden w-[85%] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/10 p-4 backdrop-blur md:block">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Analitik agen waktu nyata & pagar pengaman SLA</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-200/80">Pantau CSAT, backlog, dan cakupan otomatisasi dari satu dasbor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-b border-slate-100 bg-white py-10 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-gray-950">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-screen-xl flex-col gap-6 px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-slate-500">Dipercaya oleh tim pemasaran, layanan pelanggan, dan pertumbuhan di</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 text-base font-semibold text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500">
      {logos.map((logo) => (
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-300">
          {logo}
        </span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-slate-50 py-24 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-700 dark:bg-sky-500/20 dark:text-sky-100">Transformasi Digital</span>
      <h2 class="mt-6 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">Mengapa AI Custom Penting untuk Bisnis Anda</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        Di era digital yang serba cepat, bisnis yang tidak beradaptasi akan tertinggal. Kecerdasan Buatan (AI) bukan lagi teknologi futuristik—ini adalah kebutuhan strategis yang dapat membedakan Anda dari kompetitor. Namun, solusi AI generik sering kali gagal memenuhi kebutuhan unik setiap bisnis.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition hover:-translate-y-1 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sky-100 dark:bg-sky-500/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Efisiensi Operasional</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Otomatisasi tugas berulang dapat menghemat hingga 40% waktu kerja tim Anda. AI custom dirancang khusus untuk proses bisnis Anda, memastikan integrasi yang seamless dengan sistem existing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition hover:-translate-y-1 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-500/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Keputusan Berbasis Data</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Analitik prediktif dan dashboard real-time memberikan insight actionable untuk decision-making yang lebih cepat dan akurat. Prediksi tren pasar, perilaku pelanggan, dan performa bisnis dengan presisi tinggi.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition hover:-translate-y-1 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-500/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Pengalaman Pelanggan Superior</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Chatbot cerdas dan personalisasi content meningkatkan engagement hingga 300%. Layanan 24/7 dengan response time instan menciptakan customer satisfaction yang luar biasa.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition hover:-translate-y-1 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-rose-100 dark:bg-rose-500/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-rose-600 dark:text-rose-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">ROI Terukur</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Investasi AI custom menghasilkan ROI positif dalam 6-12 bulan. Reduksi biaya operasional, peningkatan revenue, dan competitive advantage yang sustainable adalah outcome yang dapat diukur dan dilacak.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition hover:-translate-y-1 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-500/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Skalabilitas & Keamanan</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Infrastruktur cloud-native yang scalable memastikan sistem Anda tumbuh seiring bisnis. Enkripsi end-to-end dan compliance dengan standar internasional (GDPR, ISO 27001) menjaga data Anda tetap aman.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition hover:-translate-y-1 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-500/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Competitive Advantage</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">First-mover advantage dalam industri Anda. AI custom memberikan diferensiasi yang sulit ditiru kompetitor, memposisikan bisnis Anda sebagai leader inovatif di pasar.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-24 dark:bg-gray-950">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 dark:bg-emerald-500/20 dark:text-emerald-100">Metodologi Kami</span>
      <h2 class="mt-6 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">Proses Implementasi yang Terbukti Efektif</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        Kami mengikuti framework implementasi yang telah teruji di ratusan proyek. Setiap fase dirancang untuk meminimalkan risk, maksimalkan value, dan memastikan adoption yang sukses di organisasi Anda.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 space-y-8">
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="relative rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-slate-50 p-8 shadow-lg dark:border-slate-800 dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-900/80">
          <div class="mb-6 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sky-500 text-2xl font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-sky-500/50">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Discovery & Assessment</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Workshop mendalam untuk memahami pain points, existing systems, dan objectives bisnis Anda. Technical assessment infrastruktur dan data readiness. Hasilnya adalah roadmap detail dengan prioritization matrix dan estimated timeline.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-slate-50 p-8 shadow-lg dark:border-slate-800 dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-900/80">
          <div class="mb-6 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500 text-2xl font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/50">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Solution Design</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Desain arsitektur sistem yang scalable dan secure. Pemilihan technology stack yang optimal. Prototyping untuk validasi konsep. User journey mapping dan interface design yang intuitive untuk memastikan user adoption yang tinggi.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-slate-50 p-8 shadow-lg dark:border-slate-800 dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-900/80">
          <div class="mb-6 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-purple-500 text-2xl font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/50">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Development & Testing</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Agile development dengan sprint dua mingguan. Continuous testing dan QA di setiap iterasi. Regular demo dan feedback session untuk alignment. Model training, optimization, dan validation dengan real data dari sistem Anda.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-slate-50 p-8 shadow-lg dark:border-slate-800 dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-900/80">
          <div class="mb-6 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-rose-500 text-2xl font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-rose-500/50">4</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Deployment & Support</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Phased rollout untuk meminimalkan disruption. Comprehensive training untuk user dan admin. Monitoring dan optimization berkelanjutan. Dedicated support team dan SLA guarantee untuk peace of mind Anda.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900 py-24 text-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/20 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em]">Keunggulan Kompetitif</span>
      <h2 class="mt-6 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Bagaimana Kami Berbeda dari yang Lain</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-200">
        Banyak vendor AI menawarkan solusi "one-size-fits-all" atau hanya fokus pada teknologi tanpa memahami bisnis Anda. Kami berbeda. Berikut adalah komitmen kami yang membuat partnership bersama kami truly transformative.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 backdrop-blur-sm transition hover:bg-white/10">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sky-500/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-sky-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Business-First Approach</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-slate-300">Kami tidak mulai dari teknologi—kami mulai dari business objectives Anda. Setiap fitur yang kami develop harus tied directly ke KPI dan bottom-line impact. Technology is just the means, business value is the end.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 backdrop-blur-sm transition hover:bg-white/10">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Multidisciplinary Team</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-slate-300">Tim kami bukan hanya data scientists dan developers. Kami memiliki business consultants, UX designers, change management specialists, dan domain experts yang bekerja bersama untuk holistic solution.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 backdrop-blur-sm transition hover:bg-white/10">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-purple-500/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Full Transparency</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-slate-300">No black box. Kami percaya pada explainable AI dan full transparency dalam setiap keputusan model. Anda akan understand bagaimana sistem bekerja, apa assumptions-nya, dan bagaimana cara maintain-nya long-term.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 backdrop-blur-sm transition hover:bg-white/10">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-rose-500/20">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-rose-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
          </svg>
